<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>KI-Potenzial-Check für den Mittelstand — Ihr PDF-Report in 5 Minuten</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Finden Sie in 5 Minuten heraus, wo KI in Ihrem Unternehmen Zeit und Kosten spart. Kostenloser PDF-Report + Erstgespräch.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,400;9..144,500;9..144,600;9..144,650&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- Meta Pixel Platzhalter -->
  <script>
    // META PIXEL — EINFÜGEN BEI GO-LIVE
    // !function(f,b,e,v,n,t,s){...}(window,document,'script','https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/fbevents.js');
    // fbq('init', 'YOUR_PIXEL_ID'); fbq('track', 'PageView');
  </script>
  <noscript>
    <!-- <img height="1" width="1" style="display:none" src="https://www.facebook.com/tr?id=YOUR_PIXEL_ID&ev=PageView&noscript=1"/> -->
  </noscript>

  <!-- Google Analytics 4 Platzhalter -->
  <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=GA_MEASUREMENT_ID"></script>
  <script>
    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
    function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
    gtag('js', new Date());
    gtag('config', 'GA_MEASUREMENT_ID'); // ECHTE ID EINSETZEN
  </script>

  <style>
    :root{
      --paper:#f6f1e7;
      --paper-raised:#fffdf8;
      --ink:#1c2333;
      --muted:#5b5a6e;
      --line:#e0d8c6;
      --amber:#b8842e;
      --business:#3d4f8f;
      --business-tint:#eef0f7;
      --business-deep:#2a3a6b;
      --accent:#c75d3a;
      --accent-tint:#fdf2ed;
      --mono: 'IBM Plex Mono', ui-monospace, Menlo, monospace;
      --sans: 'IBM Plex Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
      --display: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
      --success:#1f6f5c;
      --urgent:#c0392b;
    }
    *{ margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
    html{ scroll-behavior:smooth; }
    body{
      font-family: var(--sans);
      background: var(--paper);
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    .wrap{ max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 28px; }
    a{ color: inherit; }
    :focus-visible{ outline: 3px solid var(--amber); outline-offset: 2px; }

    /* FOMO Banner */
    .fomo-banner{
      background: var(--urgent);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }
    .fomo-banner strong{ font-weight: 600; }
    .fomo-banner .pulse-dot{
      display: inline-block;
      width: 7px; height: 7px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-right: 8px;
      animation: pulse 1.6s ease-in-out infinite;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    @keyframes pulse{
      0%,100%{ opacity:1; transform:scale(1); }
      50%{ opacity:0.4; transform:scale(0.85); }
    }

    /* Masthead */
    .masthead{ border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); background: rgba(246,241,231,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(6px); }
    .masthead-inner{ display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; padding: 16px 0; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px 20px; }
    .wordmark{ font-family: var(--display); font-weight:600; font-size:1.18rem; letter-spacing:-0.01em; color: var(--ink); }
    .wordmark span{ color: var(--business); }
    .masthead nav{ display:flex; gap:22px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size:0.72rem; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color: var(--muted); }
    .masthead nav a{ text-decoration:none; }
    .masthead nav a:hover{ color: var(--ink); }
    @media (max-width: 600px){ .masthead nav{ display:none; } }

    /* Hero */
    .hero{ padding: 56px 0 44px; text-align: center; }
    .hero-eyebrow{
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size:0.74rem; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase;
      color: var(--business); margin-bottom: 18px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:10px;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow::before, .hero-eyebrow::after{
      content:""; width:24px; height:1px; background: var(--business); display:inline-block;
    }
    .hero h1{
      font-family: var(--display); font-weight:600;
      font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 5.5vw, 3.2rem);
      line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing:-0.02em;
      max-width: 18ch; margin: 0 auto 22px;
    }
    .hero h1 em{ font-style:italic; color: var(--business); font-weight:500; }
    .hero-lede{
      font-size: 1.08rem; color: var(--muted); max-width: 52ch; margin: 0 auto 32px;
    }
    .hero-badge{
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      background: var(--business-tint); color: var(--business-deep);
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.76rem; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .hero-badge svg{ width: 16px; height: 16px; }

    /* PDF Mockup SVG */
    .mockup-wrap{ display:flex; justify-content:center; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .pdf-mockup{
      width: 220px; filter: drop-shadow(0 18px 40px rgba(29,35,51,0.18));
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .pdf-mockup:hover{ transform: translateY(-6px) rotate(-1deg); }

    /* CTAs */
    .cta-primary{
      display: inline-block; background: var(--business); color: white;
      padding: 16px 36px; font-size: 1.05rem; border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s; border: none; cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(61,79,143,0.28);
    }
    .cta-primary:hover{ background: var(--business-deep); transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .cta-secondary{
      display: inline-block; background: transparent; color: var(--ink);
      padding: 14px 28px; font-size: 0.98rem; border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--line); margin-left: 12px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    }
    .cta-secondary:hover{ border-color: var(--business); background: var(--business-tint); }
    @media (max-width: 520px){
      .cta-secondary{ display: block; margin: 12px auto 0; max-width: 280px; }
    }
    .cta-note{
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    /* Social Proof Bar */
    .social-bar{
      background: var(--paper-raised); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 18px 0; text-align: center;
    }
    .social-bar-inner{ display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:center; gap: 28px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
    .social-bar .stat{ font-family: var(--display); font-weight:600; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--business); }
    .social-bar .stat-label{ font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }

    /* Sections */
    .section{ padding: 56px 0; }
    .section h2{
      font-family: var(--display); font-weight:600; font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3.2vw, 1.9rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 18px; text-align: center;
    }
    .section h2 em{ font-style:italic; color: var(--business); font-weight:500; }
    .section-intro{ text-align: center; color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.02rem; max-width: 54ch; margin: 0 auto 36px; }

    /* Problem cards */
    .problem-grid{ display:grid; gap: 16px; }
    .problem-card{
      background: var(--paper-raised); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 24px 24px 22px; display:flex; gap: 16px; align-items:flex-start;
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .problem-card:hover{ box-shadow: 0 10px 28px -12px rgba(28,35,51,0.12); border-color: var(--business); }
    .problem-icon{
      flex-shrink:0; width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:10px;
      background: var(--accent-tint); color: var(--accent);
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-weight:700; font-size:1.1rem;
      font-family: var(--display);
    }
    .problem-card h4{ font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--ink); }
    .problem-card p{ font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--muted); line-height:1.55; }

    /* Steps */
    .steps-bg{ background: var(--business-tint); }
    .step-grid{ display:grid; gap: 18px; counter-reset: step; }
    .step-card{
      background: var(--paper-raised); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 26px 24px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .step-card::before{
      counter-increment: step;
      content: counter(step);
      position: absolute; top: -10px; right: 14px;
      font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 4.5rem;
      color: var(--business); opacity: 0.06; line-height: 1;
    }
    .step-card h4{ font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--business-deep); }
    .step-card p{ font-size: 0.96rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .step-meta{
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--business);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    @media (min-width: 620px){ .step-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; } }

    /* Service preview */
    .service-card{
      background: var(--paper-raised); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 22px 20px; text-align: center; transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .service-card:hover{ box-shadow: 0 10px 28px -12px rgba(28,35,51,0.12); border-color: var(--business); }
    .service-card h4{ font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--ink); }
    .service-card p{ font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .service-grid{ display:grid; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    @media (min-width: 520px){ .service-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }

    /* Price anchor */
    .price-box{
      background: var(--ink); color: white; border-radius: 16px; padding: 36px 28px; text-align: center;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .price-box h3{ font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .price-anchor{
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-decoration: line-through;
      display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .price-real{
      font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 2.6rem; color: var(--amber); line-height: 1;
    }
    .price-real span{ font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
    .price-note{
      font-size: 0.92rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin: 14px 0 24px;
    }
    .price-savings{
      display: inline-block; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 20px;
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Trust / FAQ */
    .trust-grid{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:center; gap: 10px; list-style:none; }
    .trust-pill{
      background: var(--paper-raised); border: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--ink); display:flex; align-items:center; gap: 6px;
    }
    .trust-pill .check{ color: var(--success); font-weight: 700; }

    .faq-item{ background: var(--paper-raised); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px 24px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .faq-item h4{ font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--ink); }
    .faq-item p{ font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--muted); }

    /* Form */
    .form-section{ background: var(--paper-raised); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .lead-form{ max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: left; }
    .lead-form label{ display:block; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--sans); }
    .lead-form input, .lead-form select{
      width: 100%; padding: 14px 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; border: 1.5px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 1rem; background: white; font-family: var(--sans); color: var(--ink);
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .lead-form input:focus, .lead-form select:focus{ border-color: var(--business); outline: none; }
    .lead-form button{ width: 100%; padding: 16px; background: var(--business); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; font-family: var(--sans); transition: background 0.2s; }
    .lead-form button:hover{ background: var(--business-deep); }
    .form-disclaimer{ font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 14px; text-align: center; font-family: var(--mono); }
    .form-guarantee{
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap: 8px; margin-top: 18px;
      font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--success); font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Final CTA */
    .final-cta{ background: var(--business-deep); color: white; text-align: center; padding: 64px 0; }
    .final-cta h2{ color: white; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .final-cta p{ color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin-bottom: 28px; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .final-cta .cta-primary{ background: white; color: var(--business-deep); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.18); }
    .final-cta .cta-primary:hover{ background: var(--paper); }

    /* Footer */
    footer{ background: #141821; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); text-align: center; padding: 32px 0; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    footer a{ color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px; }
    footer a:hover{ color: white; text-decoration: underline; }

    /* Sticky CTA */
    .sticky-cta{ display: none; position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.96); padding: 12px 20px; box-shadow: 0 -4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); z-index: 90; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); backdrop-filter: blur(6px); }
    .sticky-cta a{ display: block; width: 100%; text-align: center; }
    @media (max-width: 599px){ .sticky-cta{ display: block; } body{ padding-bottom: 72px; } }

    /* Urgency timer */
    .urgency-box{
      background: var(--accent-tint); border: 1.5px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px 18px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 28px; font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .urgency-box strong{ color: var(--urgent); }

    /* Animations */
    @keyframes rise{ to{ opacity:1; transform:none; } }
    .fade-in{ opacity:0; transform: translateY(14px); animation: rise 0.7s ease-out forwards; }
    .delay-1{ animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .delay-2{ animation-delay: 0.25s; }
    .delay-3{ animation-delay: 0.4s; }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){ .fade-in{ animation: none; opacity:1; transform:none; } }
  </style>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../00-shared/themes/empire-core.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../00-shared/themes/niche-themes.css">
</head>
<body data-theme="ki-integrationen">

<!-- Masthead -->
<header class="masthead">
  <div class="wrap masthead-inner">
    <div class="wordmark">Empire<span>·</span>Expansion</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="../index.html">Verfahrensregister</a>
      <a href="#check">Check starten</a>
      <a href="#preis">Preise</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">AZ 04 · KI-Integrationen 35+</p>
    <h1 class="fade-in delay-1">Wo verliert Ihr Unternehmen <em>jede Woche Stunden?</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-lede fade-in delay-2">Finden Sie in 5 Minuten heraus, welche Prozesse sich mit KI automatisieren lassen — und was das konkret in Zeit und Geld bedeutet. Kostenlos, unverbindlich, DSGVO-konform.</p>

    <div class="hero-badge fade-in delay-2">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 7v1a7 7 0 11-4-6.5"/><polyline points="16 1 8 9 5 6"/></svg>
      12 Fragen · Individueller Score · Sofortiger PDF-Report
    </div>

    <!-- PDF Mockup SVG -->
    <div class="mockup-wrap fade-in delay-3">
      <svg class="pdf-mockup" viewBox="0 0 280 360" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <defs>
          <linearGradient id="coverGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#3d4f8f"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#2a3a6b"/>
          </linearGradient>
          <filter id="shadow" x="-20%" y="-20%" width="140%" height="140%">
            <feDropShadow dx="0" dy="8" stdDeviation="12" flood-color="rgba(29,35,51,0.18)"/>
          </filter>
        </defs>
        <!-- Back page -->
        <rect x="12" y="8" width="256" height="340" rx="10" fill="#e8e4db" transform="rotate(3 140 180)"/>
        <!-- Front page -->
        <rect x="4" y="4" width="256" height="340" rx="10" fill="url(#coverGrad)" filter="url(#shadow)"/>
        <!-- Decorative circles -->
        <circle cx="200" cy="60" r="40" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.04)"/>
        <circle cx="60" cy="300" r="50" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.03)"/>
        <!-- Top bar -->
        <rect x="4" y="4" width="256" height="6" rx="3" fill="#b8842e"/>
        <!-- Logo area -->
        <text x="32" y="52" fill="white" font-family="Georgia, serif" font-size="16" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="-0.5">Empire</text>
        <text x="32" y="70" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.6)" font-family="monospace" font-size="8" letter-spacing="1">EXPANSION</text>
        <!-- Title -->
        <text x="32" y="120" fill="white" font-family="Georgia, serif" font-size="20" font-weight="600">KI-Potenzial-</text>
        <text x="32" y="144" fill="white" font-family="Georgia, serif" font-size="20" font-weight="600">Check</text>
        <!-- Subtitle -->
        <text x="32" y="172" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.75)" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="9">Ihr persönlicher Report für den</text>
        <text x="32" y="186" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.75)" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="9">Mittelstand — in 5 Minuten</text>
        <!-- Score visualization -->
        <rect x="32" y="210" width="200" height="8" rx="4" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)"/>
        <rect x="32" y="210" width="156" height="8" rx="4" fill="#b8842e"/>
        <text x="32" y="236" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.6)" font-family="monospace" font-size="7" letter-spacing="0.5">SCORE: 78/100 · HOCHES POTENZIAL</text>
        <!-- Bottom section -->
        <rect x="32" y="260" width="200" height="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)"/>
        <text x="32" y="282" fill="white" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="10" font-weight="600">Top 3 Automatisierungsbereiche</text>
        <rect x="32" y="294" width="180" height="6" rx="3" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/>
        <rect x="32" y="308" width="140" height="6" rx="3" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/>
        <rect x="32" y="322" width="100" height="6" rx="3" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/>
        <!-- Corner fold -->
        <path d="M 220 344 L 260 344 L 260 304 Z" fill="#e0d8c6" opacity="0.3"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="fade-in delay-3">
      <a href="{{STRIPE_LINK}}" class="cta-primary">KI-Tool-Stack + Vorlagen-Set kaufen — 49 € →</a>
      <a href="lead-magnet.pdf" class="cta-secondary" download>PDF direkt laden</a>
      <p class="cta-note">30-Tage-Geld-zurück-Garantie · Sofortiger Download · DSGVO-konform</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Social Proof Bar -->
<section class="social-bar">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="social-bar-inner">
      <div><div class="stat">12</div><div class="stat-label">Fragen im Check</div></div>
      <div><div class="stat">30</div><div class="stat-label">Tage Garantie</div></div>
      <div><div class="stat">49 €</div><div class="stat-label">KI-Tool-Stack</div></div>
      <div><div class="stat">299 €</div><div class="stat-label">Individuelles Setup</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Problem Section -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>Klingt das <em>bekannt?</em></h2>
    <p class="section-intro">Die meisten Mittelständler verlieren 10–20 Stunden pro Woche an Aufgaben, die längst automatisiert sein könnten.</p>
    <div class="problem-grid">
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-icon">1</div>
        <div>
          <h4>Anfragen gehen verloren</h4>
          <p>E-Mails, WhatsApp und Anrufe außerhalb der Bürozeiten. Manche bleiben unbeantwortet — und damit Aufträge liegen.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-icon">2</div>
        <div>
          <h4>Ihr Team ist mit Routine überlastet</h4>
          <p>Terminabsprachen, FAQs, Dokumente sortieren, Daten einpflegen. Stunden, die für wichtigere Arbeit fehlen.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <div class="problem-icon">3</div>
        <div>
